Don't worry. I have a plan.

601
00:40:20.626 --> 00:40:24.916
<i>I wanted to run far away to a place</i>

602
00:40:25.005 --> 00:40:27.675
<i>where those people don't exist.</i>

603
00:40:27.758 --> 00:40:32.008
